  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil.",
    "Add the pasta and cook until al dente. Drain and set aside.",
    "In a saucepan, mix heavy cream with softened garlic.",
    "Over medium heat, add butter, parmesan cheese, salt, pepper, and all-purpose flour to form a roux. Cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cooked pasta and cream mixture to the sauce, mixing well until smooth and heated through.",
    "Top with grated lamination puff (cornmeal dough coated in egg wash) cut into circles and baked until golden brown.",
    "Serve immediately."
